asual at\\u00e9 um evento mais formal. Eles combinam perfeitamente com acess\\u00f3rios neutros ou vibrantes, permitindo infinitas possibilidades de estilo. Adicione um vestido floral \\u00e0 sua cole\\u00e7\\u00e3o e sinta-se radiante em qualquer lugar.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Roboto Serif\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"10\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),(860,213,'_elementor_page_assets','a:1:{s:6:\"styles\";a:1:{i:0;s:12:\"e-animations\";}}'),(863,214,'_elementor_edit_mode','builder'),(864,214,'_elementor_template_type','wp-page'),(865,214,'_elementor_version','3.23.3'),(866,214,'_wp_page_template','default'),(867,214,'_elementor_data','[{\"id\":\"e594674\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"8a28256\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"editor\":\"<p><em>Bem-vindo \\u00e0 se\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\\"Moda em Destaque\\\" da Duo Fashion, onde voc\\u00ea encontra as \\u00faltimas tend\\u00eancias que est\\u00e3o dominando o mundo da moda. Nossa curadoria apresenta as pe\\u00e7as mais quentes da esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o, incluindo vestidos com estampas florais que exalam frescor e romantismo, blazers oversized que combinam eleg\\u00e2ncia e descontra\\u00e7\\u00e3o, e as nost\\u00e1lgicas cal\\u00e7as cargo que retornam dos anos 90 e 2000.<\\/em><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"text_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Roboto Serif\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow\":{\"horizontal\":0,\"vertical\":0,\"blur\":0,\"color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.3)\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"67961bc\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"con