\\/Prancheta-3-6.png\\\" class=\\\"elementor-animation-grow attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-269\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-b43a3d6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\\\" data-id=\\\"b43a3d6\\\" data-element_type=\\\"container\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-404bd48 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\\\" data-id=\\\"404bd48\\\" data-element_type=\\\"widget\\\" data-widget_type=\\\"image.default\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-widget-container\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\\"187\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/10.26.45.27\\/duo_fashion\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/08\\/Prancheta-4-5.png\\\" class=\\\"elementor-animation-grow attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-270\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-a6afd7f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\\\" data-id=\\\"a6afd7f\\\" data-element_type=\\\"container\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"e-con-inner\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-b96c9bb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\\\" data-id=\\\"b96c9bb\\\" data-element_type=\\\"widget\\\" data-widget_type=\\\"text-editor.default\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-widget-container\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>As camisetas V-neck, ou camisetas com decote em V, s\\u00e3o conhecidas por seu estilo moderno e favorecedor, proporcionando um toque de sofistica\\u00e7\\u00e3o aos looks casuais. O decote em V alonga visualmente o pesco\\u00e7o e destaca a clav\\u00edcula, sendo uma escolha popular tanto para homens quanto para mulheres. Dispon\\u00edveis em uma variedade de cores e materiais, como algod\\u00e3o e malha, essas camisetas s\\u00e3o ideais para combinar com cal\\u00e7as jeans, saias ou at\\u00e9 mesmo usar por baixo de blazers. As camisetas V-neck s\\u00e3o perfeitas para quem busca conforto e um toque de eleg\\u00e2ncia no dia a dia.<\\/p>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-3bfa6e1 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\\\" data-id=\\\"3bfa6e1\\\" data-element_type=\\\"container\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"e-con-inner\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-572188c elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\\\" data-id=\\\"572188c\\\" data-element_type=\\\"widget\\\" data-widget_type=\\\"heading.default\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-widget-container\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2 class=\\\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\\\">Camisetas Tie-Dye<\\/h2>\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-8cd24a0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\\\" data-id=\\\"8cd24a0\\\" data-element_type=\\\"container\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"e-con-inner\\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-89c351f e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\\\" data-id=\\\"89c351f\\\" data-element_type=\\\"container\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-element elementor-element-738571c elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\\\" data-id=\\\"738571c\\\" data-element_type=\\\"widget\\\" data-widget_type=\\\"image.default\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"elementor-widget-container\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\\"187\\\" height=\\\"300\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/10.26.45.27\\/duo_fashion\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/08\\/Prancheta-1-7.png\\\" class=\\\"elementor-animation-grow attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-274\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\