esses sapatos apresentam designs cl\\u00e1ssicos e atemporais, como oxfords, derbies e mocassins. Eles s\\u00e3o perfeitos para usar em ambientes profissionais, eventos formais e ocasi\\u00f5es especiais, proporcionando um toque final de sofistica\\u00e7\\u00e3o ao traje. Confort\\u00e1veis e elegantes, os sapatos sociais s\\u00e3o um s\\u00edmbolo de bom gosto e estilo, combinando perfeitamente com ternos, blazers e vestidos formais.<\\/p>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\",\"scripts\":[],\"styles\":[\"e-animations\"]}}'),(2528,470,'_edit_last','1'),(2529,470,'_edit_lock','1723126849:1'),(2530,470,'_thumbnail_id','285'),(2531,470,'_regular_price','169.00'),(2532,470,'_sale_price','125.50'),(2533,470,'total_sales','0'),(2534,470,'_tax_status','taxable'),(2535,470,'_tax_class',''),(2536,470,'_manage_stock','yes'),(2537,470,'_backorders','no'),(2538,470,'_sold_individually','no'),(2539,470,'_virtual','no'),(2540,470,'_downloadable','no'),(2541,470,'_download_limit','-1'),(2542,470,'_download_expiry','-1'),(2543,470,'_stock','5'),(2544,470,'_stock_status','instock'),(2545,470,'_wc_average_rating','0'),(2546,470,'_wc_review_count','0'),(2547,470,'_product_version','9.1.4'),(2548,470,'_price','125.50'),(2549,462,'_eael_post_view_count','3'),(2550,471,'_elementor_edit_mode','builder'),(2551,471,'_elementor_template_type','wp-page'),(2552,471,'_elementor_version','3.23.4'),(2553,471,'_wp_page_template','default'),(2554,471,'_elementor_data','[{\"id\":\"192af52\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"516403a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"content_width\":\"full\",\"title\":\"Camisetas\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#000000\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Roboto Serif\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"600\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"040e21d\",\"elT